ZH: 我在地上铺盖了一床毯子。
EN: I laid a blanket on the ground.

ZH: 爸爸帮我铺盖被子。
EN: Dad helped me put on the bed covers.

ZH: 冬天来了，我要铺盖被子睡觉。
EN: Winter is here, I need to cover myself with a blanket to sleep.

ZH: 奶奶给我准备了一床新的铺盖。
EN: Grandma prepared a new set of bedding for me.

ZH: 弟弟没有铺盖，我把我的给了他。
EN: My younger brother didn't have bedding, so I gave him mine.

ZH: 我在沙滩上铺盖了一块毛巾。
EN: I laid a towel on the beach.

ZH: 姐姐把铺盖抖得很整齐。
EN: My sister shook the bedding to make it tidy.

ZH: 他拿出几张铺盖纸，开始准备包饺子。
EN: He took out several sheets of dough to prepare the dumplings.

ZH: 妈妈做了一顿大餐，铺盖满了整个餐桌。
EN: Mom made a feast, and the table was covered with dishes.

ZH: 我们在野营的时候要自己铺盖帐篷。
EN: We need to set up our own tents when camping.

ZH: 每天早上，我都会帮爸爸整理铺盖。
EN: Every morning, I help my dad tidy up the bedding.

ZH: 需要用铺盖把宝宝捂得暖暖的。
EN: Need to use bedding to keep the baby warm.

ZH: 我的铺盖包很重，里面有很多书。
EN: My backpack of bedding is heavy, it contains many books.

ZH: 爸爸偷偷用针线修了一下我的铺盖。
EN: Dad secretly sewed a few stitches on my bedding.

ZH: 我喜欢在旅行中烹饪，铺盖总是弄得很脏。
EN: I enjoy cooking during travels, and the bedding always gets dirty.

ZH: 这家酒店的铺盖看起来很干净和舒适。
EN: The bedding in this hotel looks clean and comfortable.

ZH: 他把铺盖叠得很整齐，看起来像个大师傅。
EN: He folded the bedding neatly, resembling a professional.

ZH: 这个地方的晚上很冷，我需要多带几床铺盖。
EN: It gets very cold at night in this place, I need to bring more bedding.

ZH: 每晚睡觉之前，我都要在床上铺盖好被子。
EN: Before going to bed every night, I cover the bed with a blanket.

ZH: 出去露营时，别忘了带上铺盖和帐篷。
EN: Don't forget to bring bedding and tents when going camping.
